Extract Keys from AWS SSM Parameter Store
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Understand AWS Systems Manager Parameter Store security implications
Query and enumerate SSM parameters to identify stored secrets
Identify common misconfigurations in parameter permissions
Automate parameter extraction using Python
Recognize security vulnerabilities in cloud parameter storage
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of AWS services and IAM concepts
Familiarity with Linux command line operations
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of JSON data structures
