Key Findings to Identify
Plaintext storage of sensitive data (Type: String instead of SecureString)
Overly descriptive parameter names revealing system architecture
Weak credentials stored in parameters
Parameters with multiple versions (potential secret rotation issues)
Missing encryption on sensitive configuration
Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: JSON parsing errors when loading parameters

Solution: Validate JSON syntax using python3 -m json.tool filename.json
Check for trailing commas or missing quotes
Issue: Script cannot find parameters directory

Solution: Verify current working directory with pwd
Use absolute paths: os.path.abspath(parameters_dir)
Issue: Empty results from enumeration

Solution: Confirm .json files exist in parameters directory
Check file permissions with ls -la parameters/
